title: Spacious layouts and high ceilings, Quartz slab countertops, Pet Spa
posting_body: ['Welcome to The Landing', 'At The Landing apartments, there’s an effortlessness here that comes from connection – to the vibrant Dogpatch neighborhood, to a multitude of commute options, to your friends and neighbors.', 'A sense of purpose born out of thoughtful design.', 'Where the day begins with sunrise over the Bay, and ends with stargazing from the rooftop.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Glass enclosed shower', 'Energy efficient washer and dryer in unit', 'Bike Repair Station', 'Built in roller shades', 'Curated Gatherings & Community Events', 'HIIT Fitness Center', 'Pet Friendly Apartments', 'Quartz slab countertops', 'Weekly Instructed Fitness Classes', 'Open gourmet kitchen', 'Keyless Entry', 'Smeg stainless steel kitchen appliances', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Check out the virtual tour: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
